   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>... must be kept in bed ... they carried off all (we?) had in my house, which I will disclose at the specified time. Wherefore I request you that they be brought before you for fitting punishment. Farewell. Petosiris, aged about 43 years, without distinguishing marks. The second year of Imperator Nerva Caesar Augustus, Sebastos 3.</ab>
